Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.44,0:00:12.56,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,KID
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.61,0:00:17.06,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,木户吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.60,0:00:20.36,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,众多受欢迎的网络服务
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.40,0:00:23.70,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,而得到快速发展的网络服务商 M.A.R.S.公司的共同代表
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.76,0:00:25.49,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,木户明信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.53,0:00:29.95,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,被指对于在互联网中收集的个人信息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.97,0:00:32.60,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,有不正当使用的重大嫌疑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.82,0:00:43.74,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.76,0:00:47.16,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,我是M.A.R.S.社的木户明信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.69,0:00:50.33,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,请问编辑主编高野在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.11,0:00:55.45,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,从那以后17年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.92,0:00:58.52,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,围绕着游戏的环境变化很大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:02.28,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,制造商陆续发表着下一代游戏机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:06.66,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,互联网的普及更加促进了游戏的巨大变化
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.73,0:01:08.65,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,电视游戏机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.81,0:01:09.77,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,家庭用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.87,0:01:10.64,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,携带电话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.38,0:01:14.12,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,游戏 完全作为我们生活的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.14,0:01:15.94,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,成为了不可或缺的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.86,0:01:17.57,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.75,0:01:20.60,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,那样亲密的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.20,0:01:22.75,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,从那之后 没再见过面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.30,0:01:25.73,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,各自过着自己的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.70,0:01:39.78,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,攻略路线错误
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.79,0:01:43.32,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,如果有那个笔记的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:46.75,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,太空战机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.12,0:01:48.25,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,啊 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.56,0:01:49.46,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.09,0:01:52.00,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,有那个的话 就全部解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:02.00,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.02,0:02:04.67,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,笔记啊 笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.84,0:02:06.91,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,找攻略笔记啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.49,0:03:12.91,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,有件事情 想拜托高野
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.11,0:03:17.68,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,希望你代替我查明礼治的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:21.33,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,然后 把那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:22.05,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.69,0:03:24.27,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,想把它收回
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.98,0:03:27.48,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,我的攻略笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.55,0:03:32.40,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.45,0:03:40.97,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,倒闭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.03,0:03:49.31,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,喂喂 木户
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:52.60,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,现在 我已经到了渡边游戏厅了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.09,0:03:55.05,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,但是 有点想要调查的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.84,0:03:56.97,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,现在 把照片给你传过去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:06.19,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,野野村 成为了那的债权人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:15.88,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,朱理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.95,0:04:18.65,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,哎呀 好久不见了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.45,0:04:20.92,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,来见我老公的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:22.17,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:24.90,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,礼治和我结婚了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:26.90,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,结婚了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:27.84,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:31.63,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,但是 很遗憾他现在出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:34.34,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,反正又是到游戏厅那种地方去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.80,0:04:38.98,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,周转巨额不正当资金
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:40.60,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,成为被搜查对象的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.62,0:04:43.90,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,M.A.R.S.社公司的共同代表 木户明信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:45.79,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,目前下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:49.97,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,根据M.A.R.S.公司野野村社长的公布
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:54.74,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,报告已经确认木户所持有的终端设备不正当使用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.91,0:04:57.32,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,让我们继续关注他的动向
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:40.17,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,大叔 没有旋律的感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.56,0:05:47.18,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,多嘴 我听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.94,0:05:49.81,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,礼治
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:53.58,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,是礼治吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:56.99,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,你是 高野吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:05:59.23,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,好久不见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.28,0:06:01.94,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,一点没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:03.53,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,仍然和以前一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.73,0:06:06.99,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,找我什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.37,0:06:10.69,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,我一直在找你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:13.53,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,就咱们两个人说话行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:15.88,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.14,0:06:31.54,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,那儿 有笔记吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.19,0:06:33.39,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,非常遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.50,0:06:38.60,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,但是 叫渡边的游戏中心的原店主的下落找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.17,0:06:41.96,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.05,0:06:46.03,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,很好 现在马上跟着他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:50.54,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,是啊 从那以后发生了很多事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.32,0:06:54.42,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,彼此彼此吧 你不也一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:06:56.78,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,我还是和以前一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.58,0:07:00.97,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,一直工作啊工作 十多年转眼就过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.11,0:07:04.78,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,我一直是什么都没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:08.10,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,但是 那是你的梦想吧 杂志的编辑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.35,0:07:09.80,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,不是很好么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.89,0:07:13.58,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,木户的话 实现了梦想成了有钱人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.18,0:07:16.51,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,你们不都很好么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.49,0:07:20.85,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,结婚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.22,0:07:22.69,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,我见到朱理了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:25.40,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,啊 差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:28.93,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,一眨眼就过了这么多年了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.84,0:07:33.49,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,我以为你还在经营那家机厅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.38,0:07:39.17,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,我虽然也想那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:42.74,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,倒闭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.01,0:07:44.36,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,我也去了那了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:48.93,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,已经是17年前的事儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:51.53,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,那 找我什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.62,0:07:54.19,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,不可能只是来找我叙旧的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:08:00.20,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,我们需要你的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.65,0:08:03.89,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,跟我来 带上木户的笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:05.81,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.66,0:08:09.23,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,而且什么笔记本 我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.74,0:08:10.74,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,礼治
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.83,0:08:13.88,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,我和木户绝交了 所以不会再见他了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.62,0:08:17.06,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,但是 我们不是伙伴么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:20.65,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,话说你们觉得我是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.84,0:08:23.69,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,我可是负债累累临近离婚的中年大叔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:27.62,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,但是 现在只有礼治可以救他了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:30.88,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,有钱人的危机和我有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:33.93,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,浑身债务已经让我精疲力竭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.10,0:08:34.90,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,礼治
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:37.73,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,求求你了 帮帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.06,0:08:39.02,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,KID
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.01,0:08:41.01,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,在等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:46.01,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,你不也是 看了木户的新闻 想要钱么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:51.55,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,你真是个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:54.34,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,高野
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:09:00.76,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,我确实有点太混蛋了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.26,0:09:16.97,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,请问是渡边礼治先生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.63,0:09:23.28,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,好久不见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.98,0:09:30.20,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.20,0:09:51.78,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,最起码说说经过嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:53.72,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,我很担心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:56.91,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:10:00.22,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,那么 取材怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.54,0:10:01.72,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,进展顺利么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.69,0:10:04.11,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:06.51,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,还不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.89,0:10:10.20,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,但请相信 我取材的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.72,0:10:12.24,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,都是有用的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:14.68,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:19.48,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,真是一点没变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.62,0:10:22.18,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,真是的 那你就随意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:24.52,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.88,0:10:25.98,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,与此相对的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.07,0:10:29.05,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,一定要写出最好的报导哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.18,0:10:29.90,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:33.48,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,社长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:34.98,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:37.21,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,其实
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.81,0:10:41.39,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,这次取材结束后 我打算辞职
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:43.54,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,怎么了 突然这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:45.13,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,你到底在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:48.19,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,有一件一直想要做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:57.96,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.44,0:11:02.78,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,欢迎欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:08.82,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,难道 你也要木户的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.26,0:11:11.28,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,实际上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.54,0:11:14.75,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,您的朋友现在下落不明的事 您知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.04,0:11:24.29,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,他在消失之前把我们公司的主系统上了锁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:29.07,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,因此 我们无法访问Gump十分困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:31.55,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,Gump 那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.24,0:11:35.02,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,你回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.16,0:11:37.02,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,怎么样 礼治呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.65,0:11:38.60,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.85,0:11:40.83,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:44.50,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,还好他们现在还没有解开Gump的锁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:47.23,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,我们还有机会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.84,0:11:48.70,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,Gump
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.67,0:11:51.72,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,请看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.48,0:12:06.62,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,太空战机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.37,0:12:10.76,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,只有用特殊攻略把这个封顶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:15:10.76,注释,,0,0,0,Banner;15;0;80,封顶：指金额之类的数据达到上限。常用于电脑领域，尤其电视游戏、街机方面。例如得分到达「999,999,999」，在系统上无法再增加数据的情况。某些游戏并不令计数器锁定，而是从0继续开始。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.80,0:12:13.38,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,才能解开Gump的主系统的锁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.03,0:12:16.82,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,真是的 小孩子气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:19.22,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,虽然还不明白是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.24,0:12:23.57,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,这个 Gump的锁不解开的话有什么问题么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:26.41,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,是和你没有关系的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.03,0:12:29.02,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,不 也不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:33.25,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,也许是和包括你在内的全世界的人有关系的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.98,0:12:35.33,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,到底什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.45,0:12:39.77,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,曾经被称作Big Brother Echelon
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.85,0:12:41.66,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,最近 被称为Prism的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.27,0:12:45.82,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,全球间谍网络人工智能程序
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:47.70,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,那就是Gump
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.40,0:12:52.26,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,人工智能 开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:57.92,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,你知道《Fardraut Saga》吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.89,0:12:59.36,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:04.97,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,是太空战机开发小组中的一员写的小说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.54,0:13:08.42,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,其中登场叫M.A.R.S的公司
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:12.72,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,该公司开发的人工智能就叫做Gump
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.68,0:13:17.73,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,太空战机的故事是从Gump的开发开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:23.89,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,真是木户的风格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.74,0:13:29.21,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,但是 那个小说中的Gump和这个Gump是一个东西么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:31.02,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,再说 为什么木户要把那种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.84,0:13:35.04,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,Gump 是我们的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:36.68,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,还记得么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.09,0:13:38.88,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,那个机厅里的笔记本
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.76,0:13:41.28,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,攻略笔记本么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.44,0:13:42.08,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:47.04,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,游戏的乐趣不仅仅在于玩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:51.24,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,与玩同样游戏的玩家们一起玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:52.43,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,才是最大的快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:56.03,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,想要和世界上所有的玩家一起玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.42,0:13:58.37,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,想要知道他们的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.24,0:14:00.44,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,喜欢什么样的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:02.25,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,用什么样的方式玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.46,0:14:04.61,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,和什么样的同伴一起玩耍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:07.50,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,全部都想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.77,0:14:09.94,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,一下子就知道所有个人数据的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.04,0:14:12.74,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,无论是谁 都可以成为伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.15,0:14:15.60,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,开发这个程序的灵感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.72,0:14:18.93,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,就是和礼治 高野一起在机厅度过的日子里的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:20.67,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,那本攻略笔记啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:23.26,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,一瞬间检索个人数据
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:24.81,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,很厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:27.86,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,Gump就是为此而生的程序啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.04,0:14:29.62,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,只要有这个系统
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:32.05,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,我们的事业就能做得更大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:35.36,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,甚至可以与整个世界抗衡了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.82,0:14:41.82,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,感觉很厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.26,0:14:46.51,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,总觉得 木户改变了很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:49.38,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,并 并没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:50.74,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,木户
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.34,0:14:54.92,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,还是 好好和警察谈一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:57.96,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,不能这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.05,0:15:00.88,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,那些家伙 不知道什么时候会得到Gump
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.73,0:15:06.10,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,我 对木户你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.20,0:15:09.02,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,和你想的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:11.72,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,已经完全不了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.08,0:15:13.02,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,高野
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.94,0:15:17.79,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,我们已经认识30年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.16,0:15:22.37,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,已经这么久了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:28.12,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,我一直把 礼治 木户
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.10,0:15:30.70,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,当做好伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:33.55,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,一起玩游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.25,0:15:37.98,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,还曾经想 即便我们长大 也还会继续如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:40.17,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,我现在也并没
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.17,0:15:41.70,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,那是不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.10,0:15:54.94,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,您知道世界上第一个游戏是什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.78,0:15:57.50,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,怎么可能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.05,0:16:02.10,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,我只管玩游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:07.53,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,答案是Space War（太空战争）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.77,0:16:10.77,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,没错 游戏中的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:16.34,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,只是从电脑或网络中产生的玩具而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.84,0:16:19.47,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,我们的战争才是现实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.54,0:16:20.70,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,说什么混蛋话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:24.58,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,游戏不只是玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:29.31,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,游戏对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:35.15,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,是能够让我有机会交到朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:44.51,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,还是让我们来聊聊这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:47.46,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.13,0:16:49.71,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,可以把攻略笔记给我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:16:56.98,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,渡边先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.29,0:17:04.20,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,虽然你离离婚不远了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.34,0:17:06.69,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,但家人对你来说还是很重要的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:09.79,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,啊 对 什么都不是白说的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:12.35,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,让我们来谈谈价格吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.82,0:17:15.58,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,你要是把笔记给我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:20.66,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,我们会替你解决债务问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:25.78,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,那么 请快点告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.62,0:17:27.77,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,笔记的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:17:58.42,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.69,0:18:00.09,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,去哪里了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:03.00,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,那个 笔记在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.24,0:18:05.57,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,谁啊 这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.36,0:18:07.90,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,事实上 木户
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:10.74,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,我以前的兄弟被卷入了很危险的事情中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.74,0:18:12.58,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,那是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.68,0:18:14.52,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,跟我们没有关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.52,0:18:15.72,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,那个 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.79,0:18:16.50,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.52,0:18:19.34,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,如果把笔记给我们的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:23.39,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,您困扰的债务问题会帮您解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.39,0:18:23.97,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.00,0:18:27.81,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,太好了 快给他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:28.96,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,不是 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.07,0:18:32.35,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,已经从废旧的游戏厅 转移到保险柜里了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:34.19,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,那个在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:35.44,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.32,0:18:43.77,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,哎 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.62,0:18:46.59,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,朱理 这里的纸板呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.69,0:18:48.22,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,在这里的色情书
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.62,0:18:50.26,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,怎么办 扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.28,0:18:52.25,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,什么 笨蛋你扔什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.25,0:18:53.54,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,该死的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:55.37,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,哪个垃圾场
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:18:57.58,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,外面 停车场旁边的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.46,0:19:04.08,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,好像被运走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.46,0:19:07.31,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,那个 什么啊 笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.03,0:19:10.22,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,对木户很重要的笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.93,0:19:11.70,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,无论如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:13.98,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.31,0:19:19.33,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,如果是这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.79,0:19:25.10,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,你 什么 那刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.81,0:19:27.69,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,扔的只是色情书而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.53,0:19:31.71,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,而且 那个人看起来就很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.36,0:19:38.64,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,那个 野野村 到底是长什么样的笔记啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:44.48,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,朱理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.48,0:19:45.89,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,女人的直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.23,0:19:49.57,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,所以 你打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.23,0:19:54.00,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,这个东西  是从我们游戏厅开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.14,0:19:56.37,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,也应当在我们游戏厅里结束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:59.54,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,什么 游戏厅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.56,0:20:02.60,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,你们不是傻子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:07.01,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,你们这些男人 真是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:13.54,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,快去吧 如果你不早点去 那个家伙还会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.60,0:20:16.46,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.48,0:20:29.55,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,真是个笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.89,0:21:04.91,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.86,0:21:22.89,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,高野吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.69,0:21:25.18,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,请帮我转告木户
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.02,0:21:27.13,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,礼治
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.53,0:21:31.37,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,要是想要笔记的话 就让渡边来游戏厅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.08,0:21:35.24,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,和我来一场太空战机的对决
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.05,0:21:38.57,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,他要赢了 就把笔记给他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.94,0:21:41.38,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,如果 逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:44.35,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,或我赢了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.91,0:21:50.30,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,笔记就给那些家伙抵消我的债务了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.26,0:21:55.85,HideyStudio(Chinese),,0,0,0,,知道了 我帮你转告
